Property.Name: BodyScript
HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: Begin Declare @Return nvarchar(max) Select @Return = Value from core.GenericType GT join core.GenericTypeValue GTV on GTV.GenericTypeId = GT.Id join core.Resource RS on GTV.ResourceId = RS.Id join core.ResourceValue RSV on RSV.ResourceId = RS.Id where rsv.CultureId = @Culture and GTV.Id = @Value return @Return; End

Property.Name: HeaderContents
QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT Top 100 PERCENT GT.Name,RV.Value as EnglishValue,GTV.Id as GenericTypeValueId FROM [core].[GenericType] GT join [core].[GenericTypeValue] GTV on GTV.GenericTypeId = GT.Id join [core].[ResourceValue] RV on GTV.ResourceId = RV.ResourceId AND RV.CultureId = 1 --English Order By GT.Id asc
